      Found 3 categories of misalignment: v0.5 refs outside historical docs,
      old "annotation standard" title, old paper section headings.
      Left intact: paper_IT.html v0.5 sections (benchmark was run on v0.5 — historically correct),
      CHANGELOG.md (version history), nlnet drafts (historical).
      Note: codedna_setup.py UNIVERSAL_PROMPT still uses v0.4 syntax (CODEDNA:0.4,
